text: East Stroudsburg is a borough in Monroe County, Pennsylvania, United States. It lies east of Stroudsburg. East Stroudsburg is the largest municipality in Monroe County and in the East Stroudsburg, PA Metropolitan Statistical Area.Metropolitan and Micropolitan - Delineation Files - People and Households - U.S. Census Bureau . Census.gov. Retrieved on 2013-08-09. The population was 9,669 at the 2020 census. ==References== Category:Boroughs in Pennsylvania
title: East Stroudsburg, Pennsylvania
